		<title>בדיחת השבוע &#8211; 14/4</title>
		<link>http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=4333&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=%25d7%2591%25d7%2593%25d7%2599%25d7%2597%25d7%25aa-%25d7%2594%25d7%25a9%25d7%2591%25d7%2595%25d7%25a2-144</link>
